{"tid":642243,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)戰國BATMAN 地底精蟲1 5 6","createTime":"2018-04-25T15:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T19:29:03.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad9180f37904d6b61e55a5e5bc8b3357d5bc063","tid":642243,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:27:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=uCLBvvLhmdvOTtrxMbsb35WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3698263d\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=uCLBvvLhmdvOTtrxMbsb35WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a0a76ba4\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=uCLBvvLhmdvOTtrxMbsb35WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=cd9c7039\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.famitsu.hk/201712/1512121077_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.famitsu.hk%2F201712%2F1512121077_l.jpg&h=d0117ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/33/Tremorsposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F33%2FTremorsposter.jpg&h=b3b49847&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0076q8qMly1fqow3ico8cj30jt0rsn6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F0076q8qMly1fqow3ico8cj30jt0rsn6d.jpg&h=24e3fa0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.蝙蝠俠去了在阿卡漢精神病院調查時，被一神秘裝置的光芒吞噬後，時空梭從葛咸城去到戰國時代的日本。他後來發覺原來宿敵小丑也來到同一時空，更知道小丑企圖改變日本的歷史<br />\n<br />\n2.凱文貝肯&ldquo;野東西&rdquo;與佛瑞德華德是內華達州一個叫做&ldquo;完美鎮&rdquo;上的臨時工人，正當他們準備離開這個荒涼小鎮，到別處求發展時，卻發現當地居民與家畜神秘死亡的屍體，死因皆離奇怪異、不合邏輯。不久後他們赫然發現，兇手並不是什麼殺人犯，而是比殺人犯殘忍幾百倍的上千隻巨形突變怪蟲！它們潛伏在地底下，然後以迅雷不及掩耳的動作從地心竄出，吞噬地面上的人類與家畜！此時，小鎮居民陷入了恐慌之中&hellip;&hellip;他們兩人是否能幫助小鎮居民，打擊地心怪物呢？<br />\n<br />\n3.最神秘恐怖的地蟲大軍再次捲土重來！ ！大家熟悉的怪物獵人-伯特甘莫將面臨前所未有的巨蟲威脅，從有著巨大身軀的食人地蟲，以及能夠用紅外線感應生物的尖嘯蟲到會噴火飛翔的噴火巨蟲，以人肉為食的地蟲們這次再次進化，變成更致命危險的存在。在人類的搖籃-南非大地上，接連發生恐怖離奇的攻擊事件，當地人們盛傳巨獸在晚上出沒，帶著著火的尾巴，四處掠奪人命..<br />\n<br />\n4.續集在一個遠程研究站發現了Burt Gummer和他的兒子特拉維斯，在那裡他們必須抵抗已經轉化為活體武器的Graboids<br />\n<br />\n12 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=uCLBvvLhmdvOTtrxMbsb35WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=d3496b31\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=uCLBvvLhmdvOTtrxMbsb35WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6570118c\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f76b0a5c750efa2a6733aca478848759831ef3","tid":642243,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score